    "description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360770/extras/e45d4f59e1b4620ed1cf886f5de2fd5e.avif?t=1743456009\" width=601 height=85 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360770/extras/406c09d959c473c15c82547ec7b30b89.poster.avif?t=1743456009\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360770/extras/406c09d959c473c15c82547ec7b30b89.webm?t=1743456009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360770/extras/406c09d959c473c15c82547ec7b30b89.mp4?t=1743456009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在广阔遥远的星系中，一个不可阻挡的军阀带领一支舰队寻找海伯利安内核，与此同时现实世界摇摇欲坠。他们充满了难以想象的力量，掌握着救赎或毁灭的关键。你将使宇宙陷入永恒的黑暗，还是把它从危险边缘拉回来？<br><br>Coreupt 是一款快节奏的格斗游戏，融合了超快战斗和战略深度。从此星系的各个角落中，搜寻各种各样的战士，组建你的团队。其中很多人有着黑暗的秘密和复杂的故事。战场的另一边是一群同样有趣的敌人。不间断地对他们发出毁灭性连击和疾速组合攻击，从而消灭他们——要么拯救宇宙，要么彻底毁了它！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360770/extras/a95d3eeb96a43ec48be7a6e979003d05.avif?t=1743456009\" width=601 height=86 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360770/extras/ada97b8a48b6e22c35794c823995c7cd.poster.avif?t=1743456009\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360770/extras/ada97b8a48b6e22c35794c823995c7cd.webm?t=1743456009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360770/extras/ada97b8a48b6e22c35794c823995c7cd.mp4?t=1743456009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>华丽而疯狂的战斗：进行无视物理定律疾风骤雨般的疯狂战斗。使出令人瞠目结舌的连击，用令人惊叹的特殊动作点燃战场，体验向对手释放神一般力量的快感。<br></li><li>决定宇宙的命运：宇宙的命运掌握在你手中。与加特林的忠实盟友结盟以保护这个世界，或成为德拉戈诺夫的无情爪牙来改写现实世界。<br></li><li>多种游戏模式：为了满足单人和多人游戏的需求，Coreupt 提供街机、故事和生存模式。想深入了解这个传说？想真正考验你的技能？甚至可以…<br></li><li>在排行榜上竞争：随着你在排行榜上攀升，你的等级将会提升，你的名字将被载入史册。展示你的技能，赢得认可，确立你作为终极 Coreupt 冠军的统治地位</li></ul> 。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360770/extras/046de3748cef8a45018fb0043e8e85c4.avif?t=1743456009\" width=601 height=86 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360770/extras/4ac47a1acb2cd875703ecb01b7bfa5af.poster.avif?t=1743456009\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360770/extras/4ac47a1acb2cd875703ecb01b7bfa5af.webm?t=1743456009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360770/extras/4ac47a1acb2cd875703ecb01b7bfa5af.mp4?t=1743456009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Coreupt 是用虚幻引擎开发的，角色的完成度极高。每个角色在对付敌人时都会展现出自己的个性和风格。每个模型都以极高的精度进行渲染，不仅确保了游戏的顺利进行，也使人物在互殴时显得非常华丽。可以体验超过 12 个差异巨大的战士，大家都能在战士阵营中找到自己喜欢的角色!",
